MKFS_EXTRAOPTS_DOC="$(cat <<'HEREDOC'
## `--mkfs-extraopts`

This option specifies additional options to pass to the `mkfs` utility. Some default options for certain filesystems do not take effect. See Wic's help on kickstart (i.e. `wic help kickstart`).
